OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFourth teaching union      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frejects pay offer          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A teachers' union in England is to     
OL,6, ballot members on strike action after  
OL,7, 87% of its members voted to reject the 
OL,8, government's pay offer.                
OL,10,FThe NASUWT, which represents 280,000   
OL,11,Fteachers in the UK, said the offer     
OL,12,Ffailed to address its concerns over pay
OL,13,Fand working conditions.                
OL,15,FFour unions have now rejected the offer
OL,16,F- including the National Education     
OL,17,FUnion, which is planning more strikes. 
OL,19,FThe government has said further strike 
OL,20,Faction was "extremely disappointing".  
